      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior and a pristine, smoke-free cabin. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure it meets our uncompromising criteria for performance and reliability. An investment-grade opportunity for the discerning collector.",
