    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it's in such pristine condition that it still feels brand new\u2014I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it drives like a total dream! It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and it\u2019s looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. You really have to see it in person to believe how gorgeous it is. Feel free to reach out, I'd love to chat more about it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
